									<span class="tibetan-text">ཐམ་པ་</span> [tham-pa] can follow round tens and hundreds to emphasize "exactly that amount." <span class="tibetan-text">ཕྲག་</span> [trak] meaning "set" is more versatile—it can follow hundreds, thousands, and any number. For thousands and above, only <span class="tibetan-text">ཕྲག་</span> is used.
								</p>
